data.description: HONEY STOP THE CAR!!!!!! This home was redone from top to bottom and has an open layout. New roof, New duct work and insulation. New AC, hot water heater, windows and all the drywall and doors. New kitchen with shaker cabinets and granite counters. New Stainless steel appliances. Recessed lighting in the kitchen Vinyl plank flooring throughout. Bathroom has been beautifully done with a rain shower head. The large fenced in back yard is perfect for entertaining or to add a pool. The carport could be converted to a 3 bedroom and 2nd bath. This one won't last long, schedule your appointment today!
